    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_7386734539752669470.png",
                "id": "talent75133",
                "key": "煙火打揚",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "煙火打揚"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>本角色附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">庭火焰硝</span>。（此技能不產生充能）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">庭火焰硝</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">普通攻擊</span>傷害+1，造成的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>變爲<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/9fb70e06b7a56894f130c6394d8c6915_7497481929072995550.png",
                "id": "talent50748",
                "key": "焰硝庭火舞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "焰硝庭火舞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琉金火光</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">琉金火光</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>宵宮以外的我方角色使用技能後：造成一點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/26b28348d7d58e4a29a39d14cf4a81a8_1552849640844546474.png",
                "id": "talent37226",
                "key": "琉金雲間草",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "琉金雲間草"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4210774092924456946.png",
                "id": "talent39469",
                "key": "火元素傷害·其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害·其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3113405713701373011.png",
                "id": "talent30843",
                "key": "火元素傷害·其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_3624073048125978408.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害·其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/21/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7011376431417706004.png",
